    "7400407": {
        "Desc": "Feed the \"dog\"",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon wants to say that the book's contents were really weird, but it's really not much when compared to this, is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "The world should be like this, not like how it is outside. Children should be able to play under the sun and in the grass without fear of hindrance or harm."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This place does feel pretty comfy, yeah. Paimon feels way better than she did back when we were adventuring throughout the kingdom. There was no sunlight there at all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is that how it is?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "One mystery follows another."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Never mind that... This place really is nice! It's gotta be Princess Lyris's garden, right? Say, {NICKNAME}, when our adventures are over, why don't we find a place like this to live?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We can eat tasty fruits, plant lots of Sweet Flowers, and we can invite our friends over as guests! We could all live together happily. What do you say?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Eh, sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, then it's agreed! Still, we should focus on helping Ann find the Princess first, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...Let's put a pin in that for now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, that's true. We've gotta help Ann find the Princess first, don't we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mary-Ann",
                    "T": "Hide and seek, hide and seek, where did Mary and her friends go? ♪"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Sounds like someone's singing over there..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
