    "7400415": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Ann",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ann..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "#I'm sorry, Knight {NICKNAME}, Paimon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "I had already started to feel that some things were off earlier in the adventure. As you led me off the story's track, I started to understand and recall some things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "But I... still want to rescue \"Princess Lyris.\" That is the reason for which I was born. I want to save her and bring this story to a happy end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "I mean, I don't even know who she is. I only know that she is a gentle, lovely princess, trapped due to Narcissus's invasion."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Don't worry, Ann, at least... at least we had fun while traveling with the adventure team, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Um, {NICKNAME}... Did you know that things would turn out this way?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No. I thought we could help Ann."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, if that's the case, we can still help Ann."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "Huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon didn't understand anything Mary-Ann said there at the end. Did you, Ann?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "I did, sort of. I could sense that she was speaking of something terrible that happened in the past..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, Paimon feels that that's unfair — not just to you, Ann, but to us too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's why we've gotta find out what happened, at least. If we do, we can come up with some sort of plan!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Whether it be saving the Princess or figuring out what Mary-Ann said, or whatever, we just wanna help you, Ann! Isn't that right, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This \"story\" isn't over, Ann."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'll find a way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "Okay..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Still, if this is all just a story, then there's one thing Paimon doesn't get. What role do we play, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I can't be sure, but I think we're most likely..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Undefined factors."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "An accident."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And that's why we can bring this story to an end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, Paimon gets it. So that's why Ann found us and brought us into the story."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#You might not have thought about it, Ann, but since we've been able to knock this story off course, that means that we've opened all sorts of unknown possibilities. Isn't that right, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You could say that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "#*sniff* Thank you, Knight {NICKNAME}. Thank you, Paimon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's why we also need your help, Ann. And since we need to continue our adventure, well... Can you think of anything that could help us figure out what to do next?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "Hmm... Let me think..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "My memories contain a place known as the <color=#00E1FFFF>Narzissenkreuz Ordo</color>. This place appears to have very deep connections to past events."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
